<paragraph blockId="19.[178,1085,1497,1581]" pageId="19" pageNumber="1532">
Diagnosis: The members of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="OPITZ" authorityYear="2015" box="[577,668,1498,1519]" class="Insecta" family="Cleridae" genus="Isoforma" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="1555" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
