<taxonomicName authorityName="OPITZ" authorityYear="2015" box="[496,612,1559,1580]" class="Insecta" family="Cleridae" genus="Artoadenus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="1555" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[496,612,1559,1580]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="1532">Artoadenus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
they are subsecuriform.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
